item.title: CVE-2016-9591|2024-09-17T02:27:40.119Z -- jasper%20project -- jasper
item.description: JasPer before version 2.0.12 is vulnerable to a use-after-free in the way it decodes certain JPEG 2000 image files resulting in a crash on the application using JasPer.
